Mobisol announces 10 MW installed capacity milestone. Mobisol, a provider of decentralised solar solutions, has installed 10MW of solar energy to date.
 It has connected over 500,000 households in East Africa with electricity. The company based in Germany focuses on the development and supply of large solar systems that power a range of energy-efficient household and productive use appliances.
 The company plans to increase its supply of productive-use appliances for small and medium enterprises in 2018.





